OL,6,FWith the rates of epilepsy higher in
OL,7,FWales than in England, the charity is
OL,8,Fcampaigning for more Epilepsy
OL,9,FSpecialist Nurses (ESNs).
OL,11,FBecci Smart, who lives in , was
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with at the age of 18. While
OL,13,Fshe has received good care at Swansea
OL,14,FBay, she said the quality of care
OL,15,Freceived is a postcode lottery around
OL,16,FWales.
OL,18,FBecci said: "We deserve equitable care
OL,19,Fand treatment, just the same as any
OL,20,Fother person. But at the moment we are
OL,21,Fnot receiving that.
