OL,6,FHe said: "Epilepsy Action Cymru's
OL,7,Fresearch reveals a distressing reality
OL,8,Ffor those managing epilepsy in Wales.
OL,10,F"While we acknowledge that the Welsh
OL,11,FGovernment are taking some positive
OL,12,Fsteps to drive forward necessary
OL,13,Fimprovements, things are still slow to
OL,14,Fchange.
OL,16,F"Our calls to address gaps in access
OL,17,Fto services and lengthy waitings
OL,18,Fremain. People with epilepsy must get
OL,19,Fthe urgent support they need."
